reviewText: I remember watching these when I was younger and now my daughter is old enough to watch them and she absolutely loves them just as much as I did, I wish I can find the rest of them to complete my collection. So far these are the only ones sold in the USA
I really wish there were more episodes. We upgraded from our VHS to DVD on this because it was a favorite of my daughter's. We really, really would like to see new episodes.
One of a kind animation , truly a joy to watch Great for everyone...you will laugh & bond with your children with this one.
